title: Workday Healthy Routine Schedule
description:
To balance work and health after recovery, I will start implementing a new schedule:  
【Core Routine】Sleep before 22:30 on weekdays, wake up at 06:30.  
【Work Rhythm】Adopt the Pomodoro Technique (25 minutes of focus + 5 minutes of rest), with a longer break of 15–20 minutes after completing 4 Pomodoro cycles.  
【Health Integration】Take a 30-minute nap at noon and incorporate 10 minutes of stretching in the afternoon.  
【Note】This plan aims to establish a sustainable work rhythm and prevent burnout.
